Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The attack of the Nine-Tailed\NFox Demon 16 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspicion fell on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That the Uchiha had revolted\Nand sought to take power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the Uchiha was put under the strict\Nsurveillance of the Anbu Black Ops,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and they were forced to relocate\Nto the outskirts of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They became totally estranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Their distrust bred hatred and eventually,\N their suspicions became reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha clan plotted\Na coup d'état to take over the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups in Hidden Leaf Village\Nplanted a spy within the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That spy was your older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,From that moment,\NItachi's suffering began.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A coup d'état by the Uchiha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi was...a spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being an Uchiha,\Nyou were kept in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all true...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, Fugaku,\Nwas the mastermind behind the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother, Itachi, was ordered by\N your father to spy on the Anbu Black Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itachi... You also serve as {\i1}the Uchiha clan's\N pipeline {\i1}to the Village nerve center.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However...it was actually the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi was working for the village,\N feeding them information about the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was what they call\Na double agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even imagine\Nwhat a heavy burden that is to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why did Itachi betray the Uchiha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be hard for you to understand,\N not having witnessed the horrors of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Great Ninja War...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When Itachi was merely four years old,\N he witnessed the deaths of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was too young to experience war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,War is hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That trauma made Itachi\Na pacifist who hated war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man who put the village's safety first,\N and who strove to preserve peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of being bound by obligation to his clan,\N he was a ninja who loved his village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And the village higher-ups\Npreyed on that trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They assigned him to\Na top-secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For them to oppose the Uchiha,\Nthey would need the Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The total annihilation of\Nthe Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even begin to imagine\Nwhat he went through emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi was forced to make\Na terrible choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The impossible choice of killing\None's own brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But a civil war started by the likes\Nof the Uchiha would shake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the very foundations of Hidden Leaf Village\Nand the Land of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Other nations would waste no time\Nin seizing the opportunity to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It could even trigger\Na Fourth Great Ninja War...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha clan's self-interest would involve innocent\N people who had nothing to do with the ninja world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And countless people would die\Nonce again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Itachi,\Nwhat would you have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So Itachi made up his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He himself would bring\Nthe curtain down on his clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not hate the Uchiha\Nnor did he betray them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The discrimination by the village...\Nand the object of their antagonism...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldered the blame all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can ever question Itachi's decision\Nand the sacrifice he made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To be truthful, back then,\Neven I anticipated war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was bitter towards Senju's\NHidden Leaf Village as well as the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But Itachi was even aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He alone was aware\Nof my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi sought to contact me\Nand made certain conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for guiding me in my vendetta against the Uchiha,\N I was not to lay a hand on the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He would help me kill our brethren...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Third Hokage tried\Na different hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to approach the Uchiha\Nfor a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But time ran out,\Nand his efforts failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leading to that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the sole perpetrator of his clan's slaughter and\N become a Rogue Ninja with his reputation in tatters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that was his mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Itachi completely fulfilled\Nhis duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With one exception...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He could not bring himself...\Nto kill his younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.84,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(828.75,585)}Truth    \N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Itachi appealed to the Third Hokage\N to protect you from Danzo and the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he threatened Danzo\Nand left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If he laid a hand on Sasuke, he would leak every\N detail about the village to unallied nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all else,\Nhe was concerned about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet he couldn't tell you\Nthe full truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He had no choice\Nbut to say the things he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't like you, Big Brother...\N{\i1}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I acted like the older brother\N{\i1}you desired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in order to measure your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will become a rival\N{\i1}to measure my vessel against...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have that hidden potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've been jealous of me\N{\i1}and resented me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've harbored hopes\N{\i1}of surpassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is why I am allowing you to live.\N{\i1}For my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My foolish little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you wish to kill me,\N{\i1}resent me, hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And survive...in obscurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run...keep running...\N{\i1}and cling to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then one day, {\i1}come before me with\N{\i1}the same eye that I possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,By making revenge your goal,\Nhe hoped to make you strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha is a proud clan\Nof the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted you to keep\Nbelieving that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He beseeched the Hokage that\Nyou never learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And from the moment he left the village,\N he was resolved to fighting you, and dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that he could instill in you\Na new power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Itachi's truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He almost killed me several times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If Itachi wished it, he would have.\NWithout a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He even used the Mangekyo Sharingan\Nto try to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your battle was part of his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi needed to pressure you\Nin that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you probably realized it too,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, it comes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He freed you of the curse mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the death of someone\Nclosest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a battle to awaken\Nyour Mangekyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a battle that Itachi planned\Nentirely for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He pretended to be after\Nyour eyes until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to sink in, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who made the Nine-Tails attack\Nthe village was you, Madara! Itachi said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sixteen years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Madara instigated the Nine-Tails' attack\N{\i1}on Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that too was foiled\N{\i1}by the Fourth Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In short...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Madara is a bitter, defeated loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is not worthy of becoming\N{\i1}the best among the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the one... {\i1}who shall surpass Madara\N{\i1}and become the ultimate ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You framed the Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you teamed up with Itachi\Nto toy with the clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi was lying\Nwhen he told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi feared that you would\Nsomehow learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to make absolutely certain\Nthere was no chance of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He lied to make sure\Nyou would not trust me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that,\Nhe implanted Amaterasu in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He... Itachi was evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a criminal who killed his clan\Nand joined Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi took sole responsibility for\Nan unspeakable crime and left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He found a way to join Akatsuki and watched over an\N organization that was dangerous to the village from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always thinking\Nabout Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And he thought of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Third Hokage,\Nwho had promised to protect you, died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi made an appearance\Nin Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was to tell Danzo and\Nthe other superiors that "I am alive."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were foremost in his thoughts--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Lies! They're all lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to survive, we cling to all\N{\i1}we know and understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we label it reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But knowledge and understanding\N{\i1}are ambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That reality could be an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All humans live with\N{\i1}the wrong assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that another way of looking at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Sharingan...\N{\i1}How much can you actually see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My eye is not like it was in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Sharingan can see\N{\i1}through genjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humph...\N{\i1}You still speak with such confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But for now,\N{\i1}I'll take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes did not perceive\Na single thing about Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were not able to see through\Nthe illusion Itachi created at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi killed his friends, his superiors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed his lover,\Nhis father and his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But he could not kill...his little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He cried tears of blood and killed\N every shred of feeling he had inside him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then he killed his brethren\Nfor the sake of his village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But he just couldn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To him, your life...\Nwas more precious than the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the moment of his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, even in death, it was all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To pass on a new power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By making you defeat him,\Nhe had avenged the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to raise and make you\Nthe hero of Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His body was ravaged by illness\Nand he knew he was near death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he had to rely on drugs\Nto prolong his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of\Nhis beloved little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He had to fight you...\Nand die in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For the peace of Hidden Leaf Village,\Nand most of all, for Sasuke Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to die\Nas a criminal and a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepted disgrace in the place of honor,\N and hate in the place of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And despite that, Itachi died\Nwith a smile on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He entrusted the Uchiha name to you,\Nhis younger brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,deceiving you to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome home, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Play with me, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What'll we play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your brother has\N{\i1}Academy homework to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can play after he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's okay.\N{\i1}I can do my homework later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's easy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could Big Brother be hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Found you, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're pretty sharp, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother and I were playing\N{\i1}hide-and-seek today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Big Brother used Clone Jutsu\N{\i1}to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not fair, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm... You're able to do\N{\i1}the Clone Jutsu already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother, teach me\N{\i1}the Clone Jutsu too, after dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Sasuke.\N{\i1}Let's do it some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke. It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You said that you would teach me\N{\i1}a new shuriken jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have an important mission tomorrow\N{\i1}that I must prepare for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Sasuke.\N{\i1}Maybe some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother, watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey! Don't be reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you train with me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm assigned to missions {\i1}and starting tomorrow,\N {\i1}you will be attending {\i1}the Ninja Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We won't have much time\N{\i1}to spend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as you can stay with me\N{\i1}once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, we only have each other\N{\i1}as siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it's only as an obstacle\N{\i1}for you to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:19:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you help me with\N{\i1}shuriken training today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm busy.\N{\i1}You should ask Father to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you're better than Father\N{\i1}when it comes to shuriken jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even a kid like me can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oww.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Sasuke... Some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it's only as an obstacle\N{\i1}for you to overcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm always going to be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you do hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what big brothers are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are no longer "Hebi."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day on,\Nour team will be "Taka."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taka has only one goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,will destroy the Hidden Leaf.
